Ability: Get Help Choosing Between Options

  @integration
  Scenario: Skip weighing path when only one option is given
    When the Decision Support Agent attempts to seek help deciding, with:
      | Options |
      | pizza   |
    Then the Decision Support Agent should complete its workflow, as follows:
      | From  | Output                                                |
      | Agent | What are you choosing between\?                       |
      | User  | pizza                                                 |
      | Agent | Looks like you only gave me one option                |
      | Agent | the (choice\|decision) (is\|has been) (already )?made |
